    "body": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim.github.io/blob/a1259e662d0aa808e75bb96ab5d913cb459bee75/layouts/baseof.html#L21-L22\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim.github.io/blob/a1259e662d0aa808e75bb96ab5d913cb459bee75/layouts/baseof.html#L54-L55\n\n<https://docsearch.algolia.com/docs/docsearch-v3/> is dead.\n(must be <https://docsearch.algolia.com/docs/v3/docsearch/>?)\n\nv4 seems to work but rendered differently from v3, as documented.\n<https://docsearch.algolia.com/docs/migrating-from-v3#styling>:\n\n> We refreshed most of the CSS classes. The new version shouldn't break your existing styling, but more styles &amp; classes were introduced in this version so you'd probably have to customize them again.\n\n<figure>\n<img width=\"1920\" height=\"992\" alt=\"docsearch v3 vs v4\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/41f4a572-73ce-4ec9-a683-aaf3f694510c\" />\n\n<figurecaption>docsearch v3 (neovim.io) vs v4 (localhost)</figurecaption>\n</figure>",
